      &lt;img alt="Illustration of the Dish logo with a white and red background." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/V3S1wHsMyXbgHa7_sVa8f1fwxqI=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73621168/acastro_STK052_01.0.jpg" /&gt;
